Stonefish ROS2 Interface
------------------------
This project depends on stonefish_ros2, developed by Patryk Cieślak (GPL-3.0).
It is an external dependency and is NOT included in this repository.
  Repository : https://github.com/patrykcieslak/stonefish_ros2

If you use the Stonefish simulator in your research, please cite:
